ponk-protocol
=============

Copyright (c) 2026 RS Product Studio B.V.

This crate is an independent Rust implementation of the PONK ("Pathes Over
NetworK") UDP wire format, published by the Modulaser project for
interoperability.

The PONK protocol was created and published by MadMapper / GarageCube. Its
canonical public repository is:

    https://github.com/madmappersoftware/Ponk

Modulaser and ponk-protocol are not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed
by MadMapper or GarageCube. “PONK” and “MadMapper” are used descriptively to
identify the protocol and products with which this crate interoperates. All
third-party names and marks belong to their respective owners.

